data.eml:eml: Three new species of foetid Gymnopus in New Zealand

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Cooper, Jerry A., Leonard, Pat L. (2013): Three new species of foetid Gymnopus in New Zealand.
